    <h2>Fun fact</h2>
    
    <p>Did you know? India has the largest postal network in the world, with over 1,50,000 post offices, including one located on a floating structure in Dal Lake, Srinagar.</p>
    
    <img src="./dal_lake.jpg" alt="Dal lake" style="margin-left: 40px; height: 300px; width: 400px;">
    <p style="margin-left: 40px">The floating post office in Dal Lake, Srinagar</p>

